    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Please cite: Jeremy G. Frey, Samantha Pearman-Kanza, Joshua Cheung, Joanna Grundy and Matthew Partridge. Physical Chemistry Properties Data Collection. Online. 20 October 2024. Available from: https://resources.psdi.ac.uk/data/31dcd324-1574-4eeb-ba17-e8c2e9b4e0f2. [accessed YYYY-MM-DD]."^^xsd:string ;
