        <http://orcid.org/0000-0003-2583-5680>,
        <http://orcid.org/0009-0003-9952-3468> ;
    dcterms:description "This collection of datasets focuses on solubility-related information, including boiling points, Henry's law constants, LogS, melting points, and mole fractions. The Physical Chemistry Properties Data Collection provides carefully curated and standardized data on key chemical properties, empowering researchers to effectively model, analyze, and drive innovation in the field of physical chemistry. This dataset collection is available for download from a Github repository as zipped csv files."^^xsd:string ;
