    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Please cite: Leandro Liborio, Patrick Austin and Subindev Devadasan. MuSpinSim Documentation. Online. 01 August 2024. Available from: https://resources.psdi.ac.uk/guidance/95494058-7de8-4a22-9da1-c68f4497c40f. [accessed YYYY-MM-DD]."^^xsd:string ;
