        <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-1723-4394> ;
    dcterms:description "Documentation of the underlying MuSpinSim muon software tool that has been implemented as a Galaxy tool in our Galaxy instance. Muspinsim models spin dynamics calculations for muon science experiments."^^xsd:string ;
