    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Please cite \"Sturniolo, S.; Green, T. F. G.; Hanson, R. M.; Zilka, M.; Refson, K.; Hodgkinson, P.; Brown, S. P.; Yates, J. R. Visualization and Processing of Computed Solid-State NMR Parameters: MagresView and MagresPython. Solid State Nuclear Magnetic Resonance, 2016, 78, 64-70. DOI https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ssnmr.2016.05.004.\""^^xsd:string ;
    dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4485-3446> ;
    dcterms:description "MagresView provides an online interface for the Collaborative Computational Project for NMR Crystallography (CCP-NC). This visualisation tool enables crystal structure and NMR tensor visualisation from .magres files.  SSNMR parameters like magnetic shielding and electric field gradient can be displayed as scaled ellipsoids super-imposed on the crystal structure for visualisation."^^xsd:string ;
