    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Please cite: Raymond Whorley, Samantha Pearman-Kanza, Jeremy G. Frey, Donald Cruickshank, Bryan Gillis and Samuel Hyder. PSDI Data Conversion Service. Online. 31 March 2025. Available from: https://resources.psdi.ac.uk/service/8334f94b-1c6e-4034-a5ab-71c6df375cba. [accessed YYYY-MM-DD]."^^xsd:string ;
