    dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4485-3446> ;
    dcterms:description "A tool to visualize predicted NMR parameters in an intuitive, graphically accessible way and convert these parameters into input files for the most common NMR simulation programs. SSNMR parameters like magnetic shielding and electric field gradient can be visually represented as scaled ellipsoids super-imposed on the crystal structure for visualisation."^^xsd:string ;
