    dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4485-3446>,
        <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4851-1144> ;
    dcterms:description "Soprano is a Python library to help scientists working with crystallography and simulations to generate, manipulate, run calculations on and analyse large data sets of crystal structures. It provides a number of functionalities to help automate many common tasks in computational crystallography, including NMR parameter manipulation. Documentation and tutorials are provided to help users get started with the library."^^xsd:string ;
