    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Please cite: Raymond Whorley, Samantha Pearman-Kanza, Jeremy G. Frey, Donald Cruickshank, Bryan Gillis and Samuel Hyder. PSDI Data Conversion Python Library. Online. 31 March 2025. Available from: https://resources.psdi.ac.uk/tool/5ccd88f7-c182-42a1-9c55-c325ffe30039. [accessed YYYY-MM-DD]."^^xsd:string ;
