    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Please cite: Keith Butler, Bradley A. A. Martin, Cyprien Bone and Ricardo Grau-Crespo. CrystaLLM-pi (AI-driven Prediction of Crystal Structure) Github Repository. Online. 23 September 2025. Available from: https://resources.psdi.ac.uk/tool/b33b210b-93b1-495a-aa10-f38b01cd703f. [accessed YYYY-MM-DD]."^^xsd:string ;
