    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Please cite: Abraham Nieva De La Hidalga. Example Galaxy XAFS RO-Crate Workflows. Online. 26 September 2024. Available from: https://resources.psdi.ac.uk/data/f40b1d5b-2b86-4381-959b-74ec89b854c7. [accessed YYYY-MM-DD]."^^xsd:string ;
