    dcterms:description "This topic collection offers practical guidance on selecting and implementing electronic notebooks for research. It covers the benefits and challenges of adopting digital notebooks and advice on choosing the right notebook for your project. Additionally guidance is provided on considerations for moving from paper to digital and steps needed to successfully deploy an ELN solution."^^xsd:string ;
