        <http://orcid.org/0009-0000-6422-0342> ;
    dcterms:description "This course provides an introduction to the subject of ethics and research integrity. This includes details of the ethical review process, how ethics needs to be applied to data that is used for Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence. The course also provides guidance on Responsible Research and Innovation."^^xsd:string ;
