    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Please cite: Collaborative Computational Project for NMR Crystallography (CCP-NC) MAGRES Database. Online. Available from: https://www.ccpnc.ac.uk/database/. Physical Sciences Data Infrastructure (PSDI). [accessed YYYY-MM-DD]. Please also follow the citation guidelines associated with the assigned licensing of each record, including its MRD number, the creator(s) of the record and any associated publication."^^xsd:string ;
