    dcterms:creator <http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7348-7612> ;
    dcterms:description "The Physical Sciences Data Infrastructure (PSDI) is set to become the largest UK data infrastructure for the physical sciences, supporting diverse research communities in accessing and sharing data resources. Community portals are designed to provide customized access points, enabling communities to showcase the research outputs generated using PSDI's resources and services. The database, services, code, and deployed portal demonstrate the benefits of community portals, highlighting their adaptability and ease of customization and deployment for diverse research communities."^^xsd:string ;
